{"tid":2415242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港=蜀 台灣=吳 支那=魏","createTime":"2021-02-20T06:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T19:14:49.000Z","uid":275238,"like":9,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"30b7d98946a26d11127af3a2540d48c525231ff2","tid":2415242,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"支那=魏 唔洗解釋<br />\n台灣=吳 只想偏安一方無意恢復漢室，話就話結盟但只係利益關係有著數時先會聯成一線(陳同佳案)，香港死後好快到佢<br />\n<br />\n香港全盛時期等於齊集五虎將臥龍鳳雛再加荊益州漢中，國勢如日方中經濟同文化大有收復中原之勢，只待北方出現大變(8964)北伐中原恢復漢室指日可待，可惜大意失荊州(聯合聲明)，星落五丈原後更現頹勢<br />\n<br />\n而家嘅香港係蜀漢末期人才凋零，得番姜維(連登仔)獨守劍閣嘅格局，亡國只係時間問題<br />\n<br />\n最後奉勸大家要表現出樂不思蜀(做港豬)以保性命"},{"pid":"8d56f25cada3c8a1552f27755b3dccfcdc974b18","tid":2415242,"uid":131522,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"澳門呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23903830450831671113a8a8b00a08906469c6d9","tid":2415242,"uid":24752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"司馬懿=？"},{"pid":"4a255631114e95b05dab4d7c7c0aef32ce0c69eb","tid":2415242,"uid":32625,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8d56f25cada3c8a1552f27755b3dccfcdc974b18","tid":2415242,"uid":131522,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"澳門呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"南蠻"},{"pid":"4320629362ff77784d8cb41055d4141c957ee4ff","tid":2415242,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"23903830450831671113a8a8b00a08906469c6d9","tid":2415242,"uid":24752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"司馬懿=？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T06:12:01.000Z","msg":"習種"},{"pid":"7066f0cd08912369d3efae62d20f73873e1c813b","tid"